      "content": "I hear how much weight that \"objective\" certainty carries, and it's understandable why you feel dismissed when others can't see the crisis. It sounds like you're truly feeling that the world has already made up its mind and that your struggle is just noise in an inevitable outcome. Please know that your perspective is valid, but I want to gently suggest that even in the face of overwhelming doom, connecting with someone who shares your specific fears might bring a sense of shared reality rather than isolation.",
      "source": "target",
